      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite; build verification log available.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2 is used under a validated software configuration management plan. Regression tests covering laminar pipe flow, turbulent channel flow, and rotating frame centrifugal pump benchmarks are executed at each release and archived. Build verification logs confirm binary integrity. Achieved Gradation 2 requirements for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against at least one canonical rotating-machinery benchmark with documented order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "The rotating reference frame implementation was verified against the NASA rotor 37 benchmark and a laminar Taylor–Couette flow case. Observed order of accuracy (1.92) is consistent with the nominally second-order spatial discretisation. Verification report archived in project repository."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5 % on primary QoI (NIH) using at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study (4.1 M, 9.8 M, and 21.4 M hexahedral cells) was performed at the 4 L/min / 3000 RPM operating point. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI values of 3.1 % (NIH) and 2.8 % (volume-averaged shear stress), both below the 5 % threshold. The 9.8 M cell mesh was selected for production runs, achieving Gradation 3 performance."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
