      "rationale": "The FDA benchmark in vitro dataset specifies blood analogue composition (60 % glycerol/water), temperature (37 °C ± 0.5 °C), and flow rates measured with a calibrated Coriolis flow meter (±0.5 % accuracy). All five operating points are within the device's intended operating envelope. Test conditions are fully documented and traceable."
    },
    {
