      "rationale": "Validation error E% = (CFD − experiment)/experiment × 100 % was computed for NIH at all five operating points. Values ranged from −8.2 % to +11.3 %, all within the ±15 % tolerance. A validation uncertainty u_val combining experimental uncertainty and numerical uncertainty was computed following ASME V&V 20 methodology and confirmed the model is adequate for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
